{"tid":325150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英籍記者灣仔再被圍攻 白人警官：你就是「問題」","createTime":"2017-07-17T04:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T04:03:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c00f0fc0a63fd962df9d4e114a2f162984b8ecbb","tid":325150,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T04:15:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170717&amp;guid=56964273&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170717%26guid%3D56964273%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=nRMjBJKMeBZXNye%2BtwTKY26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=19a06332\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170717%26guid%3D56964273%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=079cf384\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170717&amp;guid=56964273&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">英籍記者灣仔再被圍攻 白人警官：你就是「問題」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n上月底香港民族黨集會被逼取消，演變成愛國大叔及大媽圍攻在場外籍人士，事件有下半集。當晚遭指罵的英籍公民記者Richard Scotford接著到灣仔採訪，在親中團體的集會區附近再遭圍攻指罵。警方卻要求他離開。<br />\n<br />\nRichard憶述，當時不服警方的做法，向一位白人高級警官抗議，為何被圍攻的人反而遭趕走。該警官竟回答「They have a protest permit and you are inciting them to violence(他們有示威許可，你正在煽動他們暴力)」。<br />\n<br />\nRichard反駁稱，有示威許可不代表可以用暴力。警官僅重覆稱「You are the problem, so you need to leave(你就是「問題」，所以你要離開)」。Richard批評警方既聲稱要保護記者，卻漠視有人施暴，如同暴力的共謀。<br />\n<br />\n對於Richard稱在灣仔再被圍攻一事，警方稱對每宗報案均按既定程序以認真及專業的態度處理。如有證據顯示案件涉及刑事罪行，警方會適當跟進。<br />\n<br />\n記者　潘柏林"},{"pid":"d1583b4ee43ab2ce09fb6045db204323a7820e37","tid":325150,"uid":35430,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"共化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e09281de108f798d20a0c288c0d8fc9a7984fb4","tid":325150,"uid":5922,"like":0,"disl